<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
What is easier / cost effective to heal?<BR>(IN A BATTLE THAT IS)<BR>a tank or an enchanter? I know we have less HP's so in that sence its easier, but we have less armor so we take more damage?<P>Now for a scenario:<P>Only one mob, and a normal group with a enchanter and cleric in it.<P>Enchanter casting 2 color stun spells back to back, taking an occasional hit but becuse we have little armour we recieve lots of damage.<P>If the above makes little sence to you, then let me put it this way, Would you rather us enchanters NOT color stun over and over?<P>We can always debuff instead (lots of options)<P>PS I always color stun, but I dont like it.<P>And for thoes of you that reply, would your advice apply to a lesser healer then yourselfs like druids and the like.<P>
</FONT>
