Ive grouped with a chanter that chain color stunned.  Yep I didn't have to heal with one mob.  She was the choke point of downtime though.  And er, whenever we got more than two mobs, we either died or had to evac.  Same group, same day, different chanter that mezzed primarily and used nuke/stun as appropriate and we took anything the tank could pull, chewed it up and spat it out the other end.<P>Sure, chanters are about minimizing the damage the tanks take.  But that is most effective with mezz - there is little point having the cleric fm and the chanter oom.  And by Tunare, if I have a chanter that doesnt have the mana left to mez mobs that have aggroed on me due too stunning so much they are out - permanently.
