<IMG SRC="http://206.135.232.126/eq/profile.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Profile for Jerycho"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://" target=_new><IMG SRC="http://206.135.232.126/eq/homepage.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Author's Homepage"></A> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://206.135.232.126/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=private_message&u=00014249"><IMG SRC="http://206.135.232.126/eq/priv_message.gif" BORDER='0' ALT="Send New Private Message"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://206.135.232.126/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=66&t=000006&reply_num=000018&u=00014249"><IMG SRC="http://206.135.232.126/eq/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://206.135.232.126/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=66&t=000006&replyto=000018"><IMG SRC="http://206.135.232.126/eq/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
